r smoothed plug-in\nentropy estimator. This interplay between bias analysis and approximation\ntheory is of relevance and consequence far beyond the specific problem setting\nin this paper.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 1 Feb 2015 23:27:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 10 Mar 2015 07:49:50 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 18 Sep 2017 21:01:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-20"}
