ematical model. By suitably adjusting the few parameters in the\nmodel it is possible to reproduce the basic patterns of neural activity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Feb 2015 08:39:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 24 Dec 2015 06:49:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-12-25"}
