 and further investigation in this regard is needed. This\nletter highlights that some of the clues of the early Universe can be found\nhere in our cosmic backyard.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Feb 2015 15:42:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
